1. *Zatvori* prozor, napolju je hladno. (Close the window, it's cold outside.)
2. Moramo *zatvoriti* firmu jer ne poslujemo dobro. (We have to close down the company because we are not doing well.)
3. Nije fer da *zatvorite* vrata pred nosom drugima. (It's not fair to close the door in front of others.)
4. *Zatvoriću* oči i pokušati da se opustim. (I will close my eyes and try to relax.)
5. Oni će *zatvoriti* kafić u ponoć. (They will close the cafe at midnight.)
6. Molim vas da *zatvorite* knjigu i poslušate me. (Please close the book and listen to me.)
7. Ne mogu da *zatvorim* ovu kesu, pomozi mi. (I can't close this bag, help me.)
8. Da li ste *zatvorili* prozore pre nego što ste otišli? (Did you close the windows before you left?)
9. Ako ne *zatvorimo* dogovor danas, biće kasno. (If we don't close the deal today, it will be too late.)
10. *Zatvorio* je oči i prestao da diše. (He closed his eyes and stopped breathing.)